<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Discount Hunter</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --background: #000;
            --text: #E2E8F0;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--background);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;

        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(170, 37, 242, 0.974), rgb(95, 8, 236));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;

        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;

        }

        .stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 4rem 0;

        }

        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--text);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .mission {
            padding: 6rem 0;
        }

        .mission-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;

        }

        .mission-text h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .mission-image {
            position: relative;
            height: 400px;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-image: url("./Full-Service\ Digital\ Advertising\ Technology\ &\ Management\ -\ Mediavine.jpeg");
            background-position: center;
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .cta {
            padding: 4rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.2));

        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background-color: rgb(58, 6, 140);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            background: var(--text);
            color: rgb(58, 6, 140);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .mission-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .mission-image {
                height: 300px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Unlocking Savings, Empowering Choices</h1>
                <p>We're on a mission to help people save money by finding the best deals and discounts across multiple
                    platforms and services. Our advanced platform makes it easy to discover savings opportunities you
                    might have missed.</p>
                <div class="stats">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">4.9+</div>
                        <div>Average User</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">$500+</div>
                        <div>User Savings</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">150+</div>
                        <div>Platforms Deals</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="mission">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="mission-content">
                <div class="mission-text">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>We believe everyone deserves access to the best deals available. Our platform aggregates
                        discounts from hundreds of services and platforms, making it easier than ever to save money on
                        the things you love.</p>
                    <p>Using advanced algorithms and real-time tracking, we ensure you never miss out on savings
                        opportunities. Whether it's shopping, travel, or digital services, we've got you covered.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mission-image"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to Start Saving?</h2>
            <p>Join millions of smart shoppers who save money every day</p>
            <a href="#" class="button">Get Started Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>